515
00:21:34,416 --> 00:21:36,083
We can make them relevant again!

516
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:39,041
Agreed. I believe putting
our heads together

517
00:21:39,125 --> 00:21:40,416
will make all the difference!

518
00:21:41,833 --> 00:21:43,000
[phone ringing]

519
00:21:43,083 --> 00:21:44,625
Hang on a sec.

520
