the Golden Dragon!

522
00:21:51,416 --> 00:21:52,625
Hey, Takamizawa!

523
00:21:53,916 --> 00:21:55,250
You guys are late, Queen.

524
00:21:55,333 --> 00:21:56,625
Where's the Golden Dragon?

525
00:21:56,708 --> 00:21:58,041
We're about to start digging.

526
00:21:58,125 --> 00:22:01,041
But first, we're gonna
